metadata.description: Reign of the Underdog is the collection of a 5 part mini series of comic books created by Lazarus Guidry an actor, writer and producer in Los Angeles. The 500 piece NFT collection will be used to help finance the upcoming animated series and give fans the opportunity to be part of the journey from script to screen! NFT holders will receive a long list of perks & utility in addition to receiving all 5 issues of the comics!
